								<div itemprop="articleBody">
		<p><strong>`GADDIEL </strong>sees large need in real-time information gathering and processing for all types of enterprises – Micro, Small, Medium and Large.  With the rich experience we have gathered in developing solutions and direct marketing, we see bright future for our products that are already developed or in the pipe-line.</p>
<p><strong>GADDIEL </strong>has the capability to collaborate with companies to develop custom applications or products and bring them to market at the right time.  By using proven open-source software, GADDIEL develops innovative products that cater to Micro, Small, Medium or Large enterprises.</p>
<p>Our focus for the future is:</p>
<ul>
<li>Business Mobile Solutions</li>
<li>Enterprise Solutions</li>
<li>Web Applications that are responsive</li>
<li>Mobile Solutions with dynamic adoptability to customer requirements</li>
<li>Consulting and Project Implementations</li>
<li>IT Facility Management</li>
<li>Data Analytics</li>
<li>Big Data</li>
</ul> 	</div>

	
